hours converting guides to html by hand. There isn't alot to say about it
but it gets the job done and its excellent. Thanks to this great program
you will now be able to read AIO online every month in exactly the same 
way you would see the guide file, no need for downloading the whole
archive just read AIO while you are online, look out for details of this
next month.

 Overall this program is well worthy of an AIO gold award. It is the 
simplest and best program of its kind, something not to be missed out
on.

